- This repo is an operational control plane for sysadmin/network-admin work.
- Project-local context belongs here; template changes do not.
- Project-local research notes, credential references, and security scope belong here.
- Security testing is defensive-only unless the project scope explicitly allows the activity.
- Target-repo local instructions still win when operating in another repository.
